WEBVTT

1
00:08:20.570 --> 00:08:24.754 
但是漫画诞生于深入、细致的思考。
But a cartoon is born from a space of deep, nuanced thinking.

2
00:08:24.778 --> 00:08:27.546 
好漫画的创作会经历反复的失败，
Creating a good cartoon involves repeated failures,

3
00:08:27.570 --> 00:08:29.463 
和一稿接一稿的修改。
draft after draft.

4
00:08:29.487 --> 00:08:31.838 
一个漫画家必须抛弃自己的忌讳，
And a cartoonist must shed their own taboos

5
00:08:31.862 --> 00:08:35.046 
通过他们的作品去引起交流，
to spark a conversation, rather than a confrontation,

6
00:08:35.070 --> 00:08:36.713 
而不是冲突。
through their work.

